node.text:
When I was younger I used to be very insecure about the way the veins stuck out in my hands. As I evolve I realize these features are a visual representation of how strong I am, and how I am truly so proud of myself. I’ve grown to love this part of me. There is strength in vulnerability,
Also shoe game crazy. 

🎞 @perllllz 

🦋 #loveyourself #forgiveyourself #mocha1s #nike #diy
